Basic Array Problems
Find the largest and smallest element in an array.
Find the second largest and second smallest element.
Reverse an array.
Find the sum of all elements in an array.
Find the missing number in an array of size N-1 with elements from 1 to N.


Sorting & Searching
Implement Bubble Sort, Selection Sort, Insertion Sort, Merge Sort, Quick Sort.
Search an element using Binary Search (Sorted Array).
Find the first and last occurrences of an element in a sorted array.
Find the Kth smallest and Kth largest element.
Sort an array of 0s, 1s, and 2s (Dutch National Flag problem).


Two Pointer & Sliding Window
Find a pair with a given sum in a sorted array (Two-pointer approach).
Move all negative numbers to one side of the array.
Find the maximum sum subarray of size K (Sliding Window).
Find the longest subarray with sum K.
Smallest subarray with sum greater than X.


Kadane’s Algorithm & Subarrays
Maximum sum subarray (Kadane’s Algorithm).
Maximum product subarray.
Find the longest subarray with equal number of 0s and 1s.
Find the subarray with the given sum (handles positive numbers).
Find the subarray with sum 0 (handles positive & negative numbers).


Prefix Sum & Hashing
Find the equilibrium index of an array.
Find the sum of all subarrays.
Check if a subarray with sum K exists (using HashMap).
Count the number of subarrays with sum equal to K.
Find the frequency of elements in an array.


Rearrangement & Modification
Rearrange an array so that arr[i] = i.
Rearrange positive and negative numbers alternatively.
Rearrange array in alternating max/min order.
Next permutation of an array.
Convert an array into a Zig-Zag fashion.


Bit Manipulation & XOR
Find the only non-repeating element where every other element repeats twice.
Find two non-repeating elements where every other element repeats twice.
Find the missing number in an array using XOR.
Find the number that appears odd times in an array.
Find the two numbers whose XOR is minimum in an array.


Matrix-Based Problems
Rotate a matrix by 90 degrees.
Transpose of a matrix.
Spiral traversal of a matrix.
Find the row with the maximum number of 1s in a binary matrix.
Search an element in a row-wise and column-wise sorted matrix.


Advanced & Hard Problems
Find the majority element (element occurring more than n/2 times).
Find the maximum length of a bitonic subarray.
Find the median of two sorted arrays of different sizes.
Find the maximum difference between two elements in an array.
Find the number of subarrays with at most K distinct elements.